  "body": "I browsed through the spec/our code, and found a few helper functions that are not yet implemented. I won't get to these for a bit as I'm currently working on writing further tests.\r\n\r\nIf you plan to work on one of the following please comment.\r\n\r\n(Does not include validator helpers)\r\n\r\n- [x] hash\r\n- [x] hashTreeRoot\r\n- [x] slotToEpoch\r\n- [ ] getPreviousEpoch\r\n- [x] getCurrentEpoch\r\n- [x] getEpochStartSlot\r\n- [x] isActiveValidator\r\n- [x] getActiveValidatorIndices\r\n- [x] getPermutedIndex\r\n- [x] split\r\n- [x] getEpochCommitteeCount\r\n- [x] getShuffling\r\n- [x] getPreviousEpochCommitteeCount\r\n- [x] getCurrentEpochCommitteeCount\r\n- [x] getNextEpochCommitteeCount\r\n- [x] getCrosslinkCommittessAtSlot\r\n- [x] getBlockRoot\r\n- [x] getRandaoMix\r\n- [x] getActiveIndexRoot\r\n- [ ] generateRoot\r\n- [x] getBeaconProposerIndex\r\n- [x] merkleRoot\r\n- [x] getAttestationParticipants\r\n- [x] isPowerOfTwo\r\n- [x] intToBytes1, intToBytes2... (to be handled by Buffer)\r\n- [ ] bytesToInt (to be handled by Buffer)\r\n- [x] getEffectiveBalance\r\n- [x] getTotalBalance\r\n- [x] getForkVersion\r\n- [x] getDomain\r\n- [x] getBitfieldBit\r\n- [ ] verifyBitfield\r\n- [ ] verifySlashableAttestation\r\n- [x] isDoubleVote\r\n- [x] isSurroundVote\r\n- [x] integerSquareRoot (intSqrt)\r\n- [x] getEntryExitEffectEpoch\r\n- [ ] blsVerify\r\n- [ ] blsVerifyMultiple\r\n- [ ] blsAggregatePubkeys\r\n- [x] validateProofOfPossession\r\n- [x] processDeposit",
